@4800 = ~Ah, yes—your arrival was foretold. A dove bearing the seal of Eldath arrived not long ago.~
@4801 = ~The tome has already been retrieved from our archives. Here it is. And should you see Fallskeeper Berendim again, extend to him both my gratitude and respect. The tinctures he provided for my ailing kin acted with remarkable precision. May Oghma’s light illuminate your path, and may the written word never fail you.~
@4802 = ~I come at the request of Fallskeeper Alatoasz Berendim from Duskwood Dell. He seeks a tome concerning the ancient elven cities of Keltormir.~
